 ID, Driver&#8217;s License, Keys<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Clothes<\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Hats: baseball, Tilley<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Sunglasses<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Zip ties<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">T-shirt<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Long-sleeved shirt<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Light fleece<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Driclime<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Puff jacket<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Rain\/wind jacket &#8211; Gore-Tex, Marmot Precip<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Underwear: poly<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Hiking shorts, zip-off legs<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Nylon long pants<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Rain pants<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Socks: Ultramax, heavy wool\/nylon blend<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Hiking shoes, boots, wading<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Gaiters<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Thongs<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Toque, neck warmer, mittens, nylon over mittens<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Miscellaneous<\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, 